      #tour.container_tour
        .row
          .tour.part1.col-10.col-offset-1
            .screen
              .content
                .tab
                  span tour
                h2 Built for makers
                p For over a decade, creative people from around the world have used Big Cartel’s simple tools and resources to build a unique online store, manage and sell their work, delight their fans and customers, and run their business their own way.
                .picture
                  .block_img.a
                  .source
                    span site:
                      a(href='#') melanie arbantes

              .content
                h2 Get down to business
                p We get it, you’re busy – so we keep it simple. We provide just the right mix of real-time stats, search engine optimization, order management, and promotional tools to get a small shop up and running with as little stress as possible.
                .picture
                  .block_img.b
                  .source
                    span site:
                      a(href='#') Swinj
        .module_image.biker
