              .content
                h2 Your shop, anywhere
                p Hit the road and take your shop with you. Our mobile-friendly site makes it easy to manage your shop from any phone or tablet, and our app for iPhone and iPad goes a step further to handle in-person sales at craft fairs, concerts, and other live events.
                .picture
